WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:03.350
Hey, good morning family. How are y'all

00:00:03.360 --> 00:00:05.950
doing today? Well, we're here again.

00:00:05.960 --> 00:00:07.190
We're going to do another

00:00:07.200 --> 00:00:09.190
prayer video for you. It's Brandon and

00:00:09.200 --> 00:00:13.310
Diana, the dynamic duo. We

00:00:13.320 --> 00:00:14.950
want to tell you a quick testimony.

00:00:14.960 --> 00:00:17.470
Braden was a part of it. Diana was

00:00:17.480 --> 00:00:19.790
pregnant with our third

00:00:19.800 --> 00:00:22.630
child and

00:00:25.480 --> 00:00:27.509
we were just getting off

00:00:27.519 --> 00:00:30.830
work and headed home.

00:00:30.840 --> 00:00:34.670
Our truck—we had an old truck that

00:00:34.680 --> 00:00:37.389
the gas gauge was broken on.

00:00:37.399 --> 00:00:40.430
Whenever you were out of

00:00:40.440 --> 00:00:42.270
gas, you were out of gas; you just didn't

00:00:42.280 --> 00:00:44.069
know because the gas gauge didn't work.

00:00:44.079 --> 00:00:46.470
I would always

00:00:46.480 --> 00:00:48.150
try to keep it full, but when you're

00:00:48.160 --> 00:00:51.029
running low on money, you can't

00:00:51.039 --> 00:00:52.709
always keep a big truck like that full

00:00:52.719 --> 00:00:57.110
of gas. I didn't realize how low

00:00:57.120 --> 00:00:59.990
we were, so we were just driving down

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:04.149
the road, going down I-35 in

00:01:04.159 --> 00:01:06.830
Oklahoma, going down I-35, and

00:01:06.840 --> 00:01:10.030
all of a sudden the

00:01:10.040 --> 00:01:11.469
engine just turned off. It started

00:01:11.479 --> 00:01:13.510
sputtering and it just turned

00:01:13.520 --> 00:01:18.390
off. I thought, 'Oh

00:01:18.390 --> 00:01:18.400
no.'Diana

00:01:18.400 --> 00:01:20.550
was sitting there pregnant, the

00:01:20.560 --> 00:01:23.069
two kids were in there, and it was hot. The

00:01:23.079 --> 00:01:25.830
air conditioner didn't work and it was

00:01:25.840 --> 00:01:28.870
probably around 100

00:01:28.870 --> 00:01:28.880
degrees.

00:01:28.880 --> 00:01:31.510
It was very, very hot.

00:01:34.040 --> 00:01:35.630
I started praying in the spirit,

00:01:35.640 --> 00:01:37.190
grabbed the wheel, and was just like,

00:01:37.200 --> 00:01:39.910
'God have mercy,'because

00:01:39.910 --> 00:01:39.920
we

00:01:39.920 --> 00:01:41.990
were on the highway

00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:43.710
in the middle of nowhere. It seemed

00:01:43.720 --> 00:01:46.109
like people were driving fast and I

00:01:46.119 --> 00:01:47.350
thought I'd have to get out

00:01:47.360 --> 00:01:50.910
and walk to the gas station

00:01:50.920 --> 00:01:52.310
several miles

00:01:52.320 --> 00:01:56.230
away. I told Diana,

00:01:56.240 --> 00:01:57.950
'I'm going to go,'even though we

00:01:57.950 --> 00:01:57.960
were

00:01:57.960 --> 00:02:00.069
far

00:02:00.079 --> 00:02:02.469
out in the country

00:02:02.469 --> 00:02:02.479
with

00:02:02.479 --> 00:02:05.510
no exits near.

00:02:05.520 --> 00:02:07.990
We were going through hills and

00:02:08.000 --> 00:02:12.110
flat plains

00:02:12.110 --> 00:02:12.120
and

00:02:12.120 --> 00:02:15.990
it was so hot. The kids were

00:02:16.000 --> 00:02:17.350
in the back seat, we were in

00:02:17.360 --> 00:02:19.110
the front,

00:02:19.110 --> 00:02:19.120
and

00:02:19.120 --> 00:02:21.309
when the car just turns

00:02:21.309 --> 00:02:21.319
off,

00:02:21.319 --> 00:02:24.390
fear hits you. I

00:02:24.390 --> 00:02:24.400
had

00:02:24.400 --> 00:02:26.229
my beautiful

00:02:26.239 --> 00:02:29.229
wife and two kids,

00:02:29.239 --> 00:02:30.589
she's pregnant,

00:02:30.599 --> 00:02:33.150
there's no air, it's 100 degrees,

00:02:33.150 --> 00:02:33.160
and I

00:02:33.160 --> 00:02:34.910
have to roll down these windows and

00:02:34.920 --> 00:02:36.270
walk

00:02:36.280 --> 00:02:37.509
for

00:02:37.519 --> 00:02:41.790
help. So I

00:02:41.790 --> 00:02:41.800
pulled

00:02:41.800 --> 00:02:43.869
off on the shoulder

00:02:43.879 --> 00:02:45.949
and all of a sudden I just started

00:02:45.959 --> 00:02:48.229
praying in the spirit. I told her,

00:02:48.239 --> 00:02:49.550
'You need to pray in the spirit. Help

00:02:49.560 --> 00:02:52.470
me, let's pray.'Even Braden,

00:02:52.480 --> 00:02:54.949
little as he was, was praying in the back

00:02:54.959 --> 00:02:57.149
seat. Megan was sitting in the back seat

00:02:57.159 --> 00:02:59.229
fussing already because she

00:02:59.239 --> 00:03:01.430
was already really overwhelmed with

00:03:01.440 --> 00:03:04.110
autism, and it was rough

00:03:04.110 --> 00:03:04.120
and

00:03:04.120 --> 00:03:06.550
hot.

00:03:06.560 --> 00:03:10.710
Braden

00:03:10.720 --> 00:03:12.430
started praying, we all started praying,

00:03:12.440 --> 00:03:13.990
and all of a

00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:17.390
sudden we felt like we got hit

00:03:17.400 --> 00:03:20.430
from behind. It shook the

00:03:20.440 --> 00:03:24.430
whole truck. It was a

00:03:24.440 --> 00:03:27.789
boom.

00:03:27.799 --> 00:03:30.789
I jerked, looked in my

00:03:30.799 --> 00:03:32.470
rearview

00:03:32.480 --> 00:03:35.470
mirror, and looked behind us

00:03:35.470 --> 00:03:35.480
thinking

00:03:35.480 --> 00:03:37.229
somebody just

00:03:37.229 --> 00:03:37.239
rear-ended

00:03:37.239 --> 00:03:41.750
us. It jolted us so much.

00:03:41.760 --> 00:03:43.949
The Lord allowed me at that time to

00:03:43.959 --> 00:03:48.350
see in the spirit, and I saw this massive

00:03:48.360 --> 00:03:52.429
angel with huge wings, like

00:03:52.439 --> 00:03:56.069
Angels in the Outfield. A massive

00:03:56.079 --> 00:03:58.830
wingspan. He grabbed ahold of that

00:03:58.840 --> 00:04:00.229
tailgate

00:04:00.239 --> 00:04:02.670
and smiled at me with these huge

00:04:02.680 --> 00:04:05.830
chubby cheeks. He

00:04:05.840 --> 00:04:07.670
grinned from ear to

00:04:07.680 --> 00:04:11.509
ear and started pushing our truck

00:04:11.519 --> 00:04:14.110
down the highway. It was all

00:04:14.120 --> 00:04:15.910
supernatural because the truck was off.

00:04:15.920 --> 00:04:17.990
How I had power

00:04:18.000 --> 00:04:20.909
steering or any kind of control

00:04:20.919 --> 00:04:24.749
over an off truck is still a

00:04:24.749 --> 00:04:24.759
miracle

00:04:24.759 --> 00:04:27.110
to me.

00:04:27.110 --> 00:04:27.120
When

00:04:27.120 --> 00:04:29.990
it first happened, I thought

00:04:32.520 --> 00:04:34.270
the car was doing

00:04:34.280 --> 00:04:37.230
some kind of sputter

00:04:37.230 --> 00:04:37.240
because

00:04:37.240 --> 00:04:39.110
I felt the

00:04:39.120 --> 00:04:42.150
jerk, but then I felt us accelerating

00:04:42.160 --> 00:04:44.590
again. That's when

00:04:44.590 --> 00:04:44.600
Brandon

00:04:44.600 --> 00:04:46.510
saw what he saw and I

00:04:46.520 --> 00:04:49.710
was like, 'Praise God!'Well, we started

00:04:49.720 --> 00:04:52.270
picking up speed. It accelerated. We

00:04:52.280 --> 00:04:55.189
went

00:04:55.199 --> 00:04:57.510
from

00:04:57.520 --> 00:05:00.830
zero

00:05:00.840 --> 00:05:03.350
to 70 miles

00:05:03.350 --> 00:05:03.360
per hour

00:05:03.360 --> 00:05:07.189
just like that.

00:05:07.199 --> 00:05:09.430
I had to turn my

00:05:09.440 --> 00:05:13.430
blinker on to re-enter the

00:05:13.440 --> 00:05:15.950
highway because we were going

00:05:15.950 --> 00:05:15.960
with

00:05:15.960 --> 00:05:19.029
such momentum. It wasn't slow;

00:05:19.039 --> 00:05:21.749
we started passing

00:05:21.759 --> 00:05:24.950
people in the left-hand lane.

00:05:24.960 --> 00:05:27.230
We were going so fast with that angel

00:05:27.240 --> 00:05:30.189
pushing us to the gas station that we

00:05:30.199 --> 00:05:33.309
started passing people in the fast lane.

00:05:35.759 --> 00:05:37.029
I

00:05:37.039 --> 00:05:38.469
looked and said, 'Hey, are you putting your

00:05:38.479 --> 00:05:41.270
foot on the gas?'He lifted his foot

00:05:41.270 --> 00:05:41.280
and

00:05:41.280 --> 00:05:43.230
said, 'I'm not

00:05:43.240 --> 00:05:45.870
pushing on it at all.'You could feel

00:05:45.880 --> 00:05:47.790
the car accelerating and

00:05:47.800 --> 00:05:50.230
the breeze blowing into the

00:05:50.240 --> 00:05:52.990
truck from the

00:05:53.000 --> 00:05:55.309
speed.

00:05:57.880 --> 00:06:00.070
I had my

00:06:00.080 --> 00:06:03.469
hazard lights on because I'm thinking

00:06:03.479 --> 00:06:06.909
people need to know.

00:06:11.350 --> 00:06:11.360
We

00:06:14.599 --> 00:06:17.070
were laughing and

00:06:17.080 --> 00:06:19.430
rejoicing

00:06:19.430 --> 00:06:19.440
in

00:06:19.440 --> 00:06:23.070
shock. It was very surreal. The

00:06:23.070 --> 00:06:23.080
angel

00:06:23.080 --> 00:06:25.029
was

00:06:30.199 --> 00:06:33.309
grabbing ahold of the tailgate, smiling

00:06:33.319 --> 00:06:35.110
from ear to ear, and I could

00:06:35.110 --> 00:06:35.120
feel it.

00:06:35.120 --> 00:06:38.350
It's

00:06:41.840 --> 00:06:43.990
one of those

00:06:44.000 --> 00:06:46.870
moments where

00:06:46.870 --> 00:06:46.880
you go,

00:06:46.880 --> 00:06:50.070
'Am I dreaming? Is this really

00:06:50.070 --> 00:06:50.080
happening?'Braden

00:06:50.080 --> 00:06:52.589
is

00:06:52.599 --> 00:06:54.390
praying in the

00:06:54.400 --> 00:06:56.469
spirit and I'm saying, 'Pray louder, pray

00:06:56.469 --> 00:06:56.479
louder!'He's

00:06:56.479 --> 00:06:58.510
yelling in tongues,

00:06:58.510 --> 00:06:58.520
Diana's

00:06:58.520 --> 00:07:00.070
praying in tongues,

00:07:01.960 --> 00:07:04.869
and we're going faster and faster.

00:07:04.879 --> 00:07:06.189
We

00:07:06.199 --> 00:07:07.909
weren't breaking the law, but we

00:07:07.909 --> 00:07:07.919
went

00:07:07.919 --> 00:07:10.270
from

00:07:10.280 --> 00:07:13.150
nothing

00:07:13.150 --> 00:07:13.160
to

00:07:13.160 --> 00:07:15.710
probably 70 miles

00:07:15.710 --> 00:07:15.720
per

00:07:15.720 --> 00:07:20.070
hour passing people. We went two

00:07:20.070 --> 00:07:20.080
and a

00:07:20.080 --> 00:07:24.070
half miles all the

00:07:24.080 --> 00:07:26.990
way down, exited the highway, and

00:07:26.990 --> 00:07:27.000
came

00:07:27.000 --> 00:07:32.189
to a stoplight. He stops the truck

00:07:32.199 --> 00:07:35.430
at the red light, we

00:07:35.440 --> 00:07:37.150
turn

00:07:37.160 --> 00:07:40.830
right, and he pushes the truck again through

00:07:40.840 --> 00:07:43.749
the stoplight.

00:07:47.599 --> 00:07:49.230
We went down another couple

00:07:49.240 --> 00:07:51.309
blocks, turned right again,

00:07:51.319 --> 00:07:53.909
and

00:07:53.919 --> 00:07:55.510
he pushed us all the way until

00:07:55.510 --> 00:07:55.520
we were

00:07:55.520 --> 00:07:57.309
in front of the

00:07:57.319 --> 00:07:59.629
gas station pump. He yanked the

00:07:59.639 --> 00:08:03.029
tailgate and stopped the

00:08:03.039 --> 00:08:06.270
truck right in front of the gas pump.

00:08:06.280 --> 00:08:08.589
Other people were

00:08:08.599 --> 00:08:11.990
pumping gas and we started screaming at

00:08:12.000 --> 00:08:15.950
the top of our lungs, 'Glory to

00:08:15.950 --> 00:08:15.960
God!'All

00:08:15.960 --> 00:08:17.909
the

00:08:17.919 --> 00:08:19.830
people at the gas pumps were looking

00:08:19.840 --> 00:08:22.510
at us like, 'What's going

00:08:22.510 --> 00:08:22.520
on?'because

00:08:22.520 --> 00:08:25.869
our windows were down.

00:08:25.879 --> 00:08:28.510
We were in such shock and awe at

00:08:28.520 --> 00:08:32.430
what God did. When

00:08:32.440 --> 00:08:34.469
we got to the gas station, we were

00:08:34.479 --> 00:08:36.310
just yelling, hooting, and

00:08:36.310 --> 00:08:36.320
hollering,

00:08:36.320 --> 00:08:39.029
celebrating what Jesus just did for

00:08:39.039 --> 00:08:41.230
us. Getting us off the highway,

00:08:41.240 --> 00:08:42.949
passing

00:08:42.949 --> 00:08:42.959
cars,

00:08:42.959 --> 00:08:44.790
getting us through the

00:08:44.800 --> 00:08:46.750
stoplights...

00:08:46.760 --> 00:08:48.670
I still

00:08:48.680 --> 00:08:51.269
look back and go, 'But

00:08:51.269 --> 00:08:51.279
God.'When

00:08:51.279 --> 00:08:56.670
we got to the

00:08:56.680 --> 00:09:00.230
pump, the angel disappeared.

00:09:00.240 --> 00:09:03.030
I put gas in the truck and

00:09:03.040 --> 00:09:06.389
everybody around us

00:09:06.399 --> 00:09:07.910
just

00:09:07.910 --> 00:09:07.920
looked

00:09:07.920 --> 00:09:09.670
at us like, 'Why are they

00:09:09.670 --> 00:09:09.680
screaming?'but

00:09:09.680 --> 00:09:11.910
we were just

00:09:11.920 --> 00:09:14.550
rejoicing. Braden will never forget

00:09:14.560 --> 00:09:17.150
it.

00:09:17.150 --> 00:09:17.160
It's

00:09:17.160 --> 00:09:21.190
amazing.

00:09:24.760 --> 00:09:28.630
When

00:09:28.640 --> 00:09:30.670
something like that happens and you're

00:09:30.680 --> 00:09:33.509
believing for a miracle,

00:09:33.509 --> 00:09:33.519
you

00:09:33.519 --> 00:09:35.310
think,

00:09:35.320 --> 00:09:37.829
'Lord, how's it going to come

00:09:46.720 --> 00:09:48.750
through?'But

00:09:54.480 --> 00:09:58.630
God,

00:09:58.640 --> 00:10:02.269
in the least expected way.

00:10:13.040 --> 00:10:15.829
We weren't expecting that at all.

00:10:17.480 --> 00:10:20.389
It was

00:10:20.399 --> 00:10:22.790
just shock and awe. I remember passing

00:10:24.870 --> 00:10:24.880
a

00:10:26.800 --> 00:10:29.389
person

00:10:29.389 --> 00:10:29.399
in

00:10:29.399 --> 00:10:30.910
a little

00:10:30.920 --> 00:10:34.350
white car

00:10:34.360 --> 00:10:35.110
and

00:10:35.120 --> 00:10:38.590
thinking, 'They don't even

00:10:40.590 --> 00:10:40.600
know.'And

00:10:43.760 --> 00:10:46.550
how I had control over the power

00:10:46.560 --> 00:10:49.389
steering—it

00:10:49.399 --> 00:10:51.430
wasn't

00:10:51.440 --> 00:10:54.150
in neutral,

00:10:54.160 --> 00:10:56.470
it was still in drive.

00:10:56.480 --> 00:10:59.550
There was no engine sound.

00:11:02.160 --> 00:11:04.509
You

00:11:04.519 --> 00:11:07.389
still try to calculate it and say,

00:11:10.200 --> 00:11:14.910
'How did that happen?'But God.

00:11:14.920 --> 00:11:16.389
When you try to wrap your mind

00:11:16.399 --> 00:11:17.470
around the

00:11:17.480 --> 00:11:19.670
supernatural,

00:11:21.560 --> 00:11:23.750
you can't; the

00:11:23.760 --> 00:11:25.750
natural man perceiveth not the things of

00:11:25.760 --> 00:11:26.790
the

00:11:26.800 --> 00:11:29.310
Lord. Even whenever He's doing something

00:11:29.320 --> 00:11:31.629
so big and so mighty,

00:11:31.639 --> 00:11:33.629
you're trying to put your intellect to

00:11:33.639 --> 00:11:35.990
the supernatural and figure out how He did

00:11:35.990 --> 00:11:36.000
that.

00:11:36.000 --> 00:11:39.670
I know the

00:11:39.680 --> 00:11:42.550
angels are real.

00:11:42.560 --> 00:11:44.150
I believe with all my heart what He

00:11:44.160 --> 00:11:46.310
said in Psalm 91: He sent His angels

00:11:46.320 --> 00:11:49.509
to protect us. But when you actually have

00:11:49.519 --> 00:11:50.590
an

00:11:50.600 --> 00:11:53.949
experience that defies the laws of

00:11:53.959 --> 00:11:57.269
everything...

00:11:57.279 --> 00:11:59.710
cars don't go down the road fast with

00:11:59.720 --> 00:12:00.750
the engine

00:12:00.760 --> 00:12:03.870
off.

00:12:11.920 --> 00:12:15.189
You go back and

00:12:15.199 --> 00:12:17.829
try to make sense of it in the

00:12:17.839 --> 00:12:20.389
natural,

00:12:20.399 --> 00:12:22.110
kind of like when she was not

00:12:22.120 --> 00:12:25.470
having any pain in birth.

00:12:30.839 --> 00:12:33.389
We believe for big, but when big

00:12:33.399 --> 00:12:36.150
shows up, it shakes

00:12:36.160 --> 00:12:38.389
you. I thought about whenever

00:12:38.399 --> 00:12:41.670
the children of Israel saw the

00:12:41.680 --> 00:12:44.829
sea open up,

00:12:44.839 --> 00:12:48.590
or the

00:12:48.600 --> 00:12:51.030
cloud by day and the fire by night.

00:12:53.639 --> 00:12:57.470
Whenever we have

00:12:57.480 --> 00:12:59.470
some kind of supernatural

00:12:59.470 --> 00:12:59.480
manifestation

00:12:59.480 --> 00:13:03.629
take place, it shakes you. I

00:13:03.639 --> 00:13:05.750
don't know if any of you

00:13:05.760 --> 00:13:08.189
have had some kind of

00:13:08.199 --> 00:13:10.189
demonstration of the

00:13:10.199 --> 00:13:13.509
glory in your household; you probably can

00:13:13.519 --> 00:13:17.189
testify to it

00:13:17.199 --> 00:13:19.829
too, because I know He's not just done it

00:13:19.839 --> 00:13:21.389
for us. People

00:13:21.399 --> 00:13:23.350
all over the world

00:13:23.360 --> 00:13:25.509
have things happen for them

00:13:25.519 --> 00:13:28.910
too.

00:13:28.920 --> 00:13:31.949
I just thought I would tell

00:13:31.959 --> 00:13:35.269
you all to believe God again for

00:13:35.279 --> 00:13:40.590
big. Don't settle for second best;

00:13:40.600 --> 00:13:43.590
believe God for the best,

00:13:43.600 --> 00:13:45.509
exceedingly abundantly above all that we

00:13:45.519 --> 00:13:48.350
dare ask or think. That was just

00:13:48.360 --> 00:13:51.670
one testimony of many we've had.

00:13:51.680 --> 00:13:54.189
Paisley praying for the

00:13:54.199 --> 00:13:57.910
dead dog,

00:13:59.839 --> 00:14:03.230
visitations,

00:14:05.920 --> 00:14:10.189
healings...

00:14:10.199 --> 00:14:12.269
but that one

00:14:12.269 --> 00:14:12.279
stands

00:14:12.279 --> 00:14:15.269
out.

00:14:15.279 --> 00:14:18.069
When

